            <PERFORMANCE_CONDITIONS>
               <P>For each residents’ magazine, to fill up to 10 pages with external advertising, working towards generating revenue for the Council.</P>
               <P>Effectively manage the advertising sales relationship between the client and the Council, ensuring that advertising projects are completed on time and on budget per quarterly edition.</P>
               <P>Provide regular, informative updates with regards to progress of sales, at a minimum of 14 days prior to the distribution date of the residents magazine.</P>
